snippet.title: Suka Vedic Astrology
snippet.description:
We all want to gain insight into the various parts of our lives whether it’s career, relationships and money. The focus of Vedic Astrology is on you, the individual, your habits and ways of thinking. This pinpoints where the issues lie whilst providing you with the wisdom to break these habits and manifest positive opportunities in your life.  

If you wish to book a reading please follow this link for my consultation list, click Story:
https://www.facebook.com/sukavedicastrology/photos/a.107948250898614/230420821984689/

Astrology is not a proven science or exact method of seeing everything in your life. It's a spiritual guidance that one may or may not accept. There is nothing definite in astrology and nothing can ever be predicted 100% accurately. I will endeavour to deliver what I see in your chart to the best of my ability.
